			<li>Associate Director, <a href="http://cml.ics.uci.edu">Center for Machine Learning and Data Mining </a></li>
			<li>Joint appointments in the Departments of <a href="http://www.biochem.uci.edu/" target="_blank">Biological Chemistry</a>, 
				<a href="http://devcell.bio.uci.edu/" target="_blank">Developmental and Cell Biology</a>, 
				<a href="http://www.stat.uci.edu/" target="_blank">Statistics</a>,
				and <a href="http://www.bme.uci.edu/" target="_blank">Biomedical Engineering</a>. </li>
			<li>Member of the <a href="http://www.calit2.net/" target="_blank">California Institute for Telecommunications and Information Technology</a></li>
			<li>Member of the <a href="http://www.imbs.uci.edu/" target="_blank">Institute for Mathematical Behavioral Sciences </a></li>
